headline: Leading Financial Institutions to Join BrokerTec Chicago for First Day of Trading
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced that Citigroup, J.P. Morgan and Morgan Stanley will be available to trade cash U.S. Treasuries on BrokerTec Chicago when it launches on October 6.

headline: Is CME Group Stock Outperforming the S&P 500?
summary: CME Group has outperformed the S&P 500 over the past year, but analysts are cautious about the stock’s prospects.
